## Next-session recommendations

1. **Wait for CI on the 5 rust fmt PRs** (#74 #48 #70 #42 #94) to confirm rustfmt-nightly pinning fixes CI on the cheap checks.
2. **Merge the SOTA PRs in order:** #49 -> #50 -> #51 (eventra), #75 -> #76 -> #77 (eyetracker), #1 (AuthKit). PR chain keeps the trait/contract stable.
3. **Add SPEC.md files** to each owned repo per agileplus-specs/ format. The external activity on `Dev\eyetracker\agileplus-specs/EYE-SOTA-00{2,3,4}/` shows the user is building the spec-driven protocol; we should align.
4. **Speed up future grade sweeps:** populate a cargo offline cache (sccache + vendor dir) so `--fast` mode finishes in seconds, not 5+min.
5. **Phase 5 candidates:** EYE-SOTA-004 (ARKit/Vision adapter), EVE-SOTA-004 (SqliteOutbox), AUT-SOTA-002 (JWT signature verifier using JWKS), AUT-SOTA-003 (WebAuthn challenge), BEN-SOTA-001 (criterion-table-formatter integration).
